posts.post_content: Hoping this is the right place to post this. I’ve been collecting Jake Stahl cards for two decades now and am approaching the end of the journey with only a few cards left. Looking for an E90-1 and three T206 - the Drum, Broadleaf 460, and Tolstoi backs. Condition does not matter, just need these last four cards and I’ll have the collection complete. PM if you have one and are looking to get rid of it or trade. I have a ton of stuff to trade as well. Thank you
You might do better if you put Jake Stahl in the title.  Also might make more sense in the T206 section since 3 of the 4 cards are t206.  Good luck.
